  "short_description": "Fight, Mine, Scavenge, Trade, Craft or Mission your way through the Anadeia Galaxy and write your name in the stars using different skills, ships, weapons and equipment, alone or on the couch with a friend in this Open-Word Sandbox RPG Space sim.",
